# Privacy Policy

This site angelomeniconi.co.uk respects your privacy. This policy explains what personal data we collect and how we use it.

## Information we collect

- **Contact form submissions**: name, email, message.  
- **Cookies/analytics**: via Google Analytics (with your consent).  

## How we use your data

- To respond to inquiries submitted via the contact form.  
- To analyze site usage and improve the website (analytics data is anonymous).

## Data sharing

- Contact form submissions are sent only to the site owner.  
- Analytics data is collected by Google only if cookies are accepted.

## Your rights

- You can request deletion of your personal data by contacting us.  
- You can disable cookies at any time via the cookie banner or browser settings.

## Contact

For questions about privacy, email: angelo.meniconi@gmail.com
